  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table bordercolor=\"#000080\">\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>So the\n        countess...</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>Closing line from John Marston's\n        masque: <em>The Entertainment of Alice, Dowager-Countess\n        of Derby</em>. Niobe is often equated with 'fallen towers',\n\tusually Rome, but here a simile with Venice is drawn. The\n\tcabinet is the actual poem, which is, like the cabinet in\n\tPoe's short story \"The Assignation\", a medley of \n\tarchitectural embellishments. </font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Enter_JM.htm\">John\n                Marston's Entertainment.</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Enter_JM.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><font>The Entertainment and\n                \"Burbank\"</font></td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Niobe</td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Cabinet</td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Structural analysis</td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "So the countess... Closing line from John Marston's masque: The Entertainment of Alice, Dowager-Countess of Derby . Niobe is often equated with 'fallen towers', usually Rome, but here a simile with Venice is drawn. The cabinet is the actual poem, which is, like the cabinet in Poe's short story \"The Assignation\", a medley of architectural embellishments. reference topics John Marston's Entertainment. The Entertainment and \"Burbank\" Niobe Cabinet Structural analysis back to \"Burbank\"",
